01:22:37.720 --> 01:22:39.230
Father, I pray for their finances

01:22:39.240 --> 01:22:41.390
tonight. There are so many people that are

01:22:41.400 --> 01:22:42.550
lacking.

01:22:42.560 --> 01:22:44.270
I pray, Father, for

01:22:53.360 --> 01:22:56.710
supernatural

01:22:56.720 --> 01:22:59.390
increase over their finances. Father, when they put their hands to something, I thank you that you said in your word that it would prosper,

01:22:59.390 --> 01:22:59.400
that they would lack no good thing. I bless them in the name of Jesus with supernatural increase over their finances.

01:22:59.400 --> 01:23:01.670
Father, this will be a

01:23:01.680 --> 01:23:05.470
time of great debt cancellation. As

01:23:05.480 --> 01:23:07.390
they go into this month, they're

01:23:07.400 --> 01:23:09.910
believing for supernatural increase,

01:23:09.920 --> 01:23:12.350
Father, with jobs and better jobs,

01:23:12.360 --> 01:23:14.790
raises and bonuses, benefits, sales and

01:23:14.800 --> 01:23:17.150
commissions, growth in business, growth

01:23:17.160 --> 01:23:19.150
in estates and inheritances, rebates and

01:23:19.160 --> 01:23:21.150
returns, checks in the mail, gifts and

01:23:21.160 --> 01:23:23.590
surprises, finding money, bills paid

01:23:23.600 --> 01:23:26.110
off, and bills decreased. We believe,

01:23:26.120 --> 01:23:28.110
Father, that this is a time for

01:23:28.120 --> 01:23:29.950
supernatural turnaround in their

01:23:29.960 --> 01:23:31.870
finances. When they look

01:23:31.880 --> 01:23:34.630
back, they'll say, 'We know, Father,

01:23:34.640 --> 01:23:36.910
our redeemer lives. Look at what the

01:23:36.920 --> 01:23:39.470
Lord has done.'In every area of our

01:23:39.470 --> 01:23:39.480
lives,

01:23:39.480 --> 01:23:42.070
we say, 'Look at what the Lord

01:23:42.080 --> 01:23:46.190
has done. He is our provider. He is

01:23:46.200 --> 01:23:49.550
Jehovah Jireh. He takes care of

01:23:49.550 --> 01:23:49.560
us.'And

01:23:49.560 --> 01:23:52.710
Father, we believe that you are the God

01:23:52.720 --> 01:23:54.910
that healeth us and provides for us.

01:23:54.920 --> 01:23:56.870
Father, this will be a time

01:23:56.880 --> 01:23:59.070
like never before to

01:23:59.080 --> 01:24:02.190
go from glory to glory.

01:24:02.200 --> 01:24:03.990
It's time

01:24:04.000 --> 01:24:06.510
for creative ideas to get wealth,

01:24:06.520 --> 01:24:09.110
creative ideas to prosper, creative

01:24:09.120 --> 01:24:11.510
ideas, Father, to spread your gospel

01:24:11.520 --> 01:24:16.190
throughout this whole world.

01:24:16.200 --> 01:24:18.230
We believe it

01:24:18.240 --> 01:24:20.470
and we receive it tonight in

01:24:20.480 --> 01:24:22.310
Jesus'name.

01:24:22.320 --> 01:24:24.910
Amen and amen. I told you I wouldn't try

01:24:24.920 --> 01:24:26.590
to keep you too long tonight, and we'll

01:24:26.600 --> 01:24:28.950
pray again tomorrow. I told you because I

01:24:28.960 --> 01:24:30.550
want you all to get up and go to church

01:24:30.560 --> 01:24:32.470
tomorrow for Easter. I don't want to

01:24:32.480 --> 01:24:33.990
keep you so you say,

01:24:33.990 --> 01:24:34.000
'Brandon, I stayed

01:24:34.000 --> 01:24:36.150
up praying too late with you,

01:24:36.160 --> 01:24:38.310
and I'm not going tomorrow

01:24:38.310 --> 01:24:38.320
morning.'Go

01:24:38.320 --> 01:24:40.070
to a local church, support it, and get

01:24:40.080 --> 01:24:42.270
excited about what God's doing. Easter

01:24:42.280 --> 01:24:44.670
Sunday is here, and it's a time that you

01:24:44.680 --> 01:24:46.590
want to be there. Don't forsake the assembling

01:24:46.600 --> 01:24:48.670
of yourselves with your brethren, and get

01:24:48.680 --> 01:24:50.870
excited about what God is doing in these

01:24:50.880 --> 01:24:53.550
last days.

01:24:53.560 --> 01:24:55.550
They need your smiling face.

01:24:55.560 --> 01:24:58.590
Go and smile. Be a light.

01:24:58.600 --> 01:25:00.230
You might sit next to a person who's

01:25:00.240 --> 01:25:02.350
coming, and they've been wayward, and

01:25:02.360 --> 01:25:04.350
they're there, and you say something to

01:25:04.360 --> 01:25:06.070
them and they're like, 'You know what?

01:25:06.080 --> 01:25:07.590
I'm glad I'm

01:25:07.590 --> 01:25:07.600
here,'just

01:25:07.600 --> 01:25:10.310
because you gave them a good smile.

01:25:10.320 --> 01:25:13.510
Be that light in the darkness.

01:25:13.520 --> 01:25:14.990
When you go out to eat tomorrow

01:25:15.000 --> 01:25:17.390
for Sunday dinner, and you go out

01:25:17.400 --> 01:25:20.070
somewhere, be a light to the waitress or

01:25:20.080 --> 01:25:21.110
waiter.

01:25:21.120 --> 01:25:23.990
Show Jesus to people,

01:25:23.990 --> 01:25:24.000
because

01:25:24.000 --> 01:25:26.270
the only Jesus people will see may

01:25:26.270 --> 01:25:26.280
be

01:25:26.280 --> 01:25:29.670
the Jesus in you and the Jesus in me.

01:25:29.680 --> 01:25:33.230
You need to be that light.

01:25:33.240 --> 01:25:35.910
Let them see Him in your eyes tomorrow.

01:25:35.920 --> 01:25:38.510
Show Jesus to the world tomorrow. If you

01:25:38.520 --> 01:25:40.350
go out to Golden Corral or something

01:25:40.350 --> 01:25:40.360
and

01:25:40.360 --> 01:25:42.950
have a big buffet, show Jesus to the

01:25:42.960 --> 01:25:44.670
waiter by not trashing the table and

01:25:44.680 --> 01:25:46.630
leaving dirty dishes. Stack them up.

01:25:46.640 --> 01:25:49.670
Make things nice. Give them a good tip and

01:25:49.670 --> 01:25:49.680
say,

01:25:49.680 --> 01:25:54.950
'Hey, we just want to love on you.'You

01:25:54.950 --> 01:25:54.960
have

01:25:54.960 --> 01:25:56.990
to show Jesus whenever you go to

01:25:57.000 --> 01:25:59.110
a drive-thru or do something. Show Jesus

01:25:59.120 --> 01:26:00.670
to people.

01:26:00.680 --> 01:26:02.950
Let them see it on you. You

01:26:02.950 --> 01:26:02.960
might say,

01:26:02.960 --> 01:26:05.110
'Hey, how are you doing today? Man,

01:26:05.120 --> 01:26:06.950
it was a rough

01:26:06.950 --> 01:26:06.960
day.'Sometimes

01:26:06.960 --> 01:26:08.750
you feel that way,

01:26:08.760 --> 01:26:13.230
but just show them Jesus.

01:26:13.240 --> 01:26:15.270
So, we love you.

01:26:15.280 --> 01:26:16.710
Maybe you have your new Easter outfit

01:26:16.720 --> 01:26:18.910
tomorrow. You wear your new clothes. My

01:26:18.920 --> 01:26:20.870
mom always used to try to get us new

01:26:20.880 --> 01:26:22.590
Easter clothes when we went to church. I

01:26:22.600 --> 01:26:24.750
told Pastor Chip, I said, 'You've got

01:26:24.760 --> 01:26:26.590
to have a new shirt for Easter. You've got

01:26:26.600 --> 01:26:29.350
to have a new coat for Easter.

01:26:29.360 --> 01:26:31.710
Wear a new jacket.

01:26:31.720 --> 01:26:34.430
Be a blessing to somebody.

01:26:34.440 --> 01:26:36.910
Let them see Jesus in you tomorrow.

01:26:36.910 --> 01:26:36.920
You've

01:26:36.920 --> 01:26:39.070
got to do

01:26:39.070 --> 01:26:39.080
it.'Maybe

01:26:39.080 --> 01:26:40.950
you go out, like I said, and

01:26:40.950 --> 01:26:40.960
you have

01:26:40.960 --> 01:26:43.590
your new slacks on and your new

01:26:43.600 --> 01:26:45.310
shirt. Maybe you have something new to wear

01:26:45.320 --> 01:26:47.550
for the Easter service. My mom always tried

01:26:47.560 --> 01:26:50.190
to do that when I was a kid. I remember

01:26:50.190 --> 01:26:50.200
getting

01:26:50.200 --> 01:26:51.150
new shoes. What are you going to wear

01:26:51.160 --> 01:26:52.910
for Easter Sunday? My sister would

01:26:52.920 --> 01:26:54.190
always get a little dress from

01:26:54.190 --> 01:26:54.200
my

01:26:54.200 --> 01:26:55.230
grandma.

01:26:55.240 --> 01:26:57.630
We'd be excited to go to

01:26:57.640 --> 01:27:00.150
church as a family and have dinner that day.

01:27:00.160 --> 01:27:04.190
Grandma would fix a meal.

01:27:04.200 --> 01:27:06.910
It's always such a beautiful time.

01:27:06.920 --> 01:27:08.550
Memories.

01:27:08.560 --> 01:27:10.830
Make memories with your kids.

01:27:10.840 --> 01:27:14.790
Make memories with your family.

01:27:14.800 --> 01:27:17.150
It's good.

01:27:17.160 --> 01:27:19.110
We love you. We're so thankful that you

01:27:19.120 --> 01:27:21.150
came tonight. I know I only kept you for

01:27:21.160 --> 01:27:23.270
an hour and a half. I didn't dip

01:27:23.280 --> 01:27:25.790
real deep in the river tonight, but it

01:27:25.790 --> 01:27:25.800
was

01:27:25.800 --> 01:27:27.830
enough where I felt okay.

01:27:27.840 --> 01:27:29.710
We covered the services and everything

01:27:29.720 --> 01:27:31.750
and just wanted to love on you. Thank

01:27:31.760 --> 01:27:33.430
you for coming. Thank you for being

01:27:33.440 --> 01:27:35.630
here. We'll pray deeper tomorrow. Diana

01:27:35.640 --> 01:27:36.990
will be with me, and we'll pray for

01:27:37.000 --> 01:27:40.710
Easter, so bring your family. We'll

01:27:40.720 --> 01:27:42.230
pray longer tomorrow. I'll come on

01:27:42.240 --> 01:27:45.710
earlier so you won't be up so late. We

01:27:45.720 --> 01:27:48.910
love y'all. Put a smile on your face and

01:27:48.920 --> 01:27:51.430
a song in your heart. Jesus loves you so

01:27:51.440 --> 01:27:53.390
much, and we love you. God bless you.

01:27:53.400 --> 01:27:56.760
Have a good night. Bye-bye.

